{"tid":2153092,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"27歲男買3隻勞力士錶中伏　遭8刀手圍毆搶走63萬元現金","createTime":"2020-08-12T10:37:24.000Z","updateTime":"2020-08-13T08:38:16.000Z","uid":7439,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"6de88035523e4b37d63fef63bf55c1cc5e983803","tid":2153092,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:37:24.000Z","msg":"事發現場 大埔泰亨鄉公所對開露天停車場<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/38a184739ee740db78defa52e0ccd1c4/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200812/_2020081208464433102.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F38a184739ee740db78defa52e0ccd1c4%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200812%2F_2020081208464433102.jpg&h=44dcaa6a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n繼上月底至本月初，尖沙咀、天水圍及大圍站多宗斬人搶錶案後。周三（12日）午夜，大埔再發生涉及買賣名錶的劫案。<span class=\"red\">1名泰亨村男村民，在村口與人交收購買3隻勞力士朱古力Daytona（地通拿）名錶期間，遭3架車圍剿、8名刀手指嚇及圍毆，載有63萬元交收現金的斜孭袋被搶去。事主被打傷，幸無刀傷，拒絕送院。</span>警方正追查事件。<br />\n <img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5042314/org/a1fdca7e57b50b561376de27a1655615.jpg/dw1Sns_nhEwRxuzECT1y-QqxSvGloNQ2caSOEFukjhA?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5042314%2Forg%2Fa1fdca7e57b50b561376de27a1655615.jpg%2Fdw1Sns_nhEwRxuzECT1y-QqxSvGloNQ2caSOEFukjhA%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=e805778a&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/5042312/org/74aecac1bd34f77411f786044565fb01.jpg/3jhyMlP7WzrCwbrF_TtUlWuMzToWhK9sNaRbtR-kW7U?v=w1920\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F5042312%2Forg%2F74aecac1bd34f77411f786044565fb01.jpg%2F3jhyMlP7WzrCwbrF_TtUlWuMzToWhK9sNaRbtR-kW7U%3Fv%3Dw1920&h=6800645a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n遇劫男子姓何（27歲），據悉泰亨村村民。今日凌晨零時許，他相約1名「賣家」，在大窩西支路近泰亨鄉公所對開露天停車場，擬購買3隻勞力士朱古力Daytona（地通拿）名錶。1名男子駕車抵達上址，事主不虞有詐，登上對方車內驗收。惟事主仍未見到名錶「真身」，即有另外2架車駛至，「賣家」即拔匙跳車逃走。<br />\n<br />\n至於8名惡煞持刀，向事主拳打腳踢圍毆，再搶走其斜孭袋，內有交收的63萬元現金，得手後原車逃去。現場消息稱，賊人逃走期間，情況混亂，有人遺下頭套、口罩及手鏈。警方調查後將案件列作「搶劫」處理；事主受皮外傷，幸無大礙，經即場治理後，拒絕送院。<br />\n<br />\n至今早約10時，探員重返現場調查案件。泰亨鄉村長文先生表示，泰亨村沒有人從事手錶買賣生意。他估計，今次案件的疑犯認識遇劫的27歲男子，<span class=\"red\">「一睇就知班人（涉案人士）係識㗎啦，要事先知道對方有60幾萬係身先犯案！」</span><br />\n<br />\n上月23日晚，尖沙咀加連威老道1間鐘錶店男東主，遭4名南亞漢毆劫，搶走其手上1隻約值140萬元Richard Mille名錶；本月1日凌晨，23歲青年天水圍鳳降村被4賊斬10刀，搶走1隻值約160萬元的Richard Mille名錶；本月4日，回港避疫的澳洲工程師，在人潮如鯽的東鐵大圍站與「買家」交收手錶，遭2男狂斬，掠走值約27萬元的勞力士Daytona玫瑰金錶。"},{"pid":"89df6c80ef67085c7fcba213a3450cc1e2311e61","tid":2153092,"uid":7439,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:38:03.000Z","msg":"警方接報趕至，在現場檢獲相信是賊人遺下的手繩、頭套、口罩。<br />\n<img src=\"https://image2.stheadline.com/f/1500p0/0x0/100/hd/60fce47d1d904227dfddc88f4495b7fa/stheadline/inewsmedia/20200812/_2020081208464350981.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimage2.stheadline.com%2Ff%2F1500p0%2F0x0%2F100%2Fhd%2F60fce47d1d904227dfddc88f4495b7fa%2Fstheadline%2Finewsmedia%2F20200812%2F_2020081208464350981.jpg&h=0116aff2&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"4224bda53b42a7338d3e20aff0ac7361e8c63c02","tid":2153092,"uid":47643,"like":17,"dislike":0,"score":17,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:39:21.000Z","msg":"勞力士梗係用勞力搶<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"59213a7884d23778a4e0c17547d23a59419e75bd","tid":2153092,"uid":283207,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:39:33.000Z","msg":"@蓋青個仔"},{"pid":"9026399cb44482ffb5ec6c989ccbb80240fa4a07","tid":2153092,"uid":48631,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:41:44.000Z","msg":"呢排想買隻casio，大拿拿成八舊水，會唔會好危險😱"},{"pid":"7f043b24731ebc85ea77e2244d9b38bb484e485a","tid":2153092,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:47:57.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"2d1f4f08bfc4e1e8bbde0164f363e97a1dab294b","tid":2153092,"uid":126621,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-12T10:48:53.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a074d296ce29c973c418916005f